  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254390/extras/8385971486a72d9f11c2833d7b6cf1b2.poster.avif?t=1673625226\" width=624 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254390/extras/8385971486a72d9f11c2833d7b6cf1b2.webm?t=1673625226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254390/extras/8385971486a72d9f11c2833d7b6cf1b2.mp4?t=1673625226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>BUILD AND MAINTAIN THE MOST ABUNDENT CORAL REEF SPA!</u></strong><br>Begin with an empty reef, as time goes on; hire cleaners, grow coral & create the best day spa in all the 7 seas!<br><br><strong><u>HIRE WORKER CREATURES!</u></strong><br>Lots of fun & hard working creatures can clean your stinky customers as super quick speeds!<br><br><strong><u>BUILD FARMS!</u></strong><br>Feed your customers and keep them happy with different farms and foods!<br><br><strong><u>UPGRADE DECORATIONS!</u></strong><br>Decorate your reef with cute lights to attract more customers & keep your workers happy!<br><br><strong><u>GROW HEALTHY CORALS!</u></strong><br>Upgrade your corals to keep the garden reef pretty & colourful!<br><br><strong><u>CARE FOR YOUR FISHY CUSTOMERS!</u></strong><br>Dirty customers need your help to get clean!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254390/extras/8385971486a72d9f11c2833d7b6cf1b2.poster.avif?t=1673625226\" width=624 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254390/extras/8385971486a72d9f11c2833d7b6cf1b2.webm?t=1673625226\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2254390/extras/8385971486a72d9f11c2833d7b6cf1b2.mp4?t=1673625226\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>BUILD AND MAINTAIN THE MOST ABUNDENT CORAL REEF SPA!</u></strong><br>Begin with an empty reef, as time goes on; hire cleaners, grow coral & create the best day spa in all the 7 seas!<br><br><strong><u>HIRE WORKER CREATURES!</u></strong><br>Lots of fun & hard working creatures can clean your stinky customers as super quick speeds!<br><br><strong><u>BUILD FARMS!</u></strong><br>Feed your customers and keep them happy with different farms and foods!<br><br><strong><u>UPGRADE DECORATIONS!</u></strong><br>Decorate your reef with cute lights to attract more customers & keep your workers happy!<br><br><strong><u>GROW HEALTHY CORALS!</u></strong><br>Upgrade your corals to keep the garden reef pretty & colourful!<br><br><strong><u>CARE FOR YOUR FISHY CUSTOMERS!</u></strong><br>Dirty customers need your help to get clean!",
